text: Phnom Penh () is one of the 25 constituencies of the National Assembly of Cambodia. It is allocated 12 seats in the National Assembly.2013 National Assembly Elections: Final Assessment and Report COMFREL It is currently the largest constituency. ==Elections== {| class=wikitable style=text-align:right !
